# 6. 道しるべの気持ち

Music Teacher: We will now begin our singing test. Starting with you, Hoshino.
Ichika: Okay.
Female Student A: I can't wait to hear Hoshino sing.
Female Student B: I know this is a test, but how cool is it that we get to hear a pro sing in person?!
Music Teacher: Ready? Begin.
Ichika: ♪———— ♪————...
Kohane: Wow...
Kohane: (Hoshino's such an incredible singer...)
Kohane: (Her voice has this intense power and beauty to it... Just listening to her makes my heart dance.)
Kohane: (Also...)
Music Teacher: That was excellent, Hoshino.
Ichika: Thank you very much.
Female Student B: That was awesome, Hoshino! Can we get an encore?!
Ichika: Haha... Thanks.
Kohane: (It's incredible how she can sing with such confidence.)
Kohane: (Confidence...)
Kohane: ... ...!
Kohane: (Why...)
Kohane: (My voice... Why can't I sing?)
Kohane: ...
Kohane: *Sob*
Kohane: Oh, my phone...
Kohane's Father's Voice: Kohane?
Kohane: ...!
Kohane: D-Dad? What's the matter...?
Kohane's Father's Voice: Umm... You looked sad for some reason when you got back.
Kohane's Father's Voice: Is everything alright...?
Kohane: Oh...
Kohane: Yes, I'm fine.
Kohane's Father's Voice: ...
Kohane's Father's Voice: I know. You should come down to the living room once you've settled down. We got sesame balls... I know they're your favorite.
Kohane: Thanks, Dad.
Kohane: (I'm so embarrassed... Everything that I've been doing...)
Kohane: (I've been causing An, Dad and a lot of other people so much worry...)
Kohane: (If...)
Kohane: (If only I had more courage...)
Music Teacher: Next, Azusawa...
Kohane: ...! R-Ready...!
Honami: You've got this, Kohane!
Kohane: Thanks...
Kohane: (Everybody's watching me...)
Kohane: (I'm so nervous...)
Kohane: (But...)
Kohane: ...————♪
Kohane: ♪———— ♪————...!
Female Student B: Whoa...! She sounds amazing!
Female Student A: Yeah! I didn't know she was such a good singer...
Kohane: ♪———— ♪————
Kohane: (I hope I don't sound too shaky...)
Kohane: (I guess I'm still...afraid of singing in front of people...)
Kohane: (Oh...)
Kohane: (I'm scared...)
Kohane: (But... I love to sing.)
Kohane: (This is the precious gift An gave me.)
Kohane: (I'm going to sing with that feeling in mind.)
Kohane: ————...♪
Music Teacher: *Nod* That was very good, Azusawa!
Kohane: Th-Thank you very much...!
Female Student A: That was amazing, Azusawa! You were so good!
Female Student B: We had no idea that you could sing like that!
Kohane: Oh, um... Thank you...
Ichika: Your voice, Azusawa... It was beautiful and sounded so crystal clear. You had me on the edge of my seat the whole time.
Kohane: Wh-What...?! Hoshino...?!
Kohane: N-No, I... I'm really nothing special...
Kohane: Oh, but I am glad that you liked my singing. And thank you for the compliment...!
Kohane: (Music class ended up being kind of fun.)
Kohane: (As nervous as I was, I managed to sing all the way until the end...)
Music Teacher: Do you have a minute, Azusawa?
Kohane: Huh? Yes, of course...
Music Teacher: I'd like to ask for a favor.
Kohane: A favor...?
Music Teacher: The thing is, the school is going to be hosting a music festival in the near future.
Music Teacher: And I'm currently looking for singers to perform at it.
Kohane: ...!
Music Teacher: You don't have to if you're not comfortable, but how would you feel about joining?
Music Teacher: I mean, the way you sang just now was absolutely spectacular.
Kohane: Oh, umm... But...
Kohane: (Singing at a music festival means performing on stage, right...?)
Kohane: (In front of a big audience...)
Kohane: I... I...
???: <...ne!>
Kohane: (Huh...?)
Kohane: (What was that just now...?)
Kohane: (That voice... It felt so familiar for some—)
Music Teacher: Azusawa?
Kohane: Oh...! I-I'm sorry...
Kohane: Umm...
Kohane: (I'm scared, but...)
Kohane: (I also want to keep moving forward.)
Kohane: I'll join...
